class Energy.Sources.Wind.Wind.WindOptimization[source]¶

Implements an assembly to contain the WindModel component, and run optimizations on it stand-alone with the pyOpt plugin of optimization drivers. Implements a caserecorder so that you can investigate the results afterwards. This assembly will show up automatically when using openmdao gui, or can be used directly in another python script as you would use a regular python class.
